EN: This squirrel likes to bury the nuts it collects in its burrow.

ZH: 我总是喜欢和你窝在一起聊天。
EN: I always enjoy snuggling up and chatting with you.

ZH: 他窝在床上想念远方的家乡。
EN: He lays in bed, missing his faraway hometown.

ZH: 这只猫很怕生，总是喜欢窝在暗处。
EN: This cat is very shy and always likes to hide in dark places.

